# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:49
translate spanish hwb_s32_482e94c5:

    # "The crowd moves on. I don't bother raising my head, allowing myself to be dragged along wherever they're going."
    "La multitud sigue adelante. No me molesto en levantar la cabeza, dejándome arrastrar hacia donde sea que vayan."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:51
translate spanish hwb_s32_24247f11:

    # "My hand is tucked deep within my pocket, playing around with the cassette and its string of tattered ribbon."
    "Tengo la mano metida en el bolsillo, jugando con el casete y su cuerda de cinta deshilachada."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:56
translate spanish hwb_s32_20b879c5:

    # "The hotel is far in the distance now, lit up against the darkening sky. Marina's probably still up there crying."
    "El hotel está muy lejos ahora, iluminado contra el cielo que oscurece. Marina probablemente sigue allá arriba llorando."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:60
translate spanish hwb_s32_1b642a81:

    # "I let go of the tape and force myself to keep walking through the clammy misters attached to shops and bars."
    "Suelto la cinta y me obligo a seguir caminando entre los vaporizadores húmedos pegados a las tiendas y bares."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:62
translate spanish hwb_s32_59db4c6a:

    # "It's not my business. It's what's best for her."
    "No es mi problema. Es lo mejor para ella."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:66
translate spanish hwb_s32_3feb98ab:

    # "But it hurts. Everything hurts."
    "Pero duele. Todo duele."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:68
translate spanish hwb_s32_1d3c35e3:

    # "I keep expecting Marina to come skip after me and lean on my shoulder so we can explore the town."
    "Sigo esperando que Marina venga saltando detrás de mí y se recargue en mi hombro para explorar el pueblo juntas."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:70
translate spanish hwb_s32_156c1ab3:

    # "Or better yet, chew me out and punch me until I feel like I can justify what I’ve done."
    "O mejor aún, que me grite y me golpee hasta que sienta que puedo justificar lo que hice."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:72
translate spanish hwb_s32_5dc34719:

    # "But I know that’s not going to happen. She’s too sweet for that. She’s Marina."
    "Pero sé que eso no va a pasar. Es demasiado dulce para eso. Es Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:74
translate spanish hwb_s32_f38df196:

    # "And I don’t want anything to ever change that. Me especially."
    "Y no quiero que nada cambie eso. Yo menos que nadie."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:76
translate spanish hwb_s32_09c041d0:

    # "I can’t be trusted with something that precious and not screw it up. Not again."
    "No se me puede confiar algo tan valioso sin arruinarlo. No otra vez."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:80
translate spanish hwb_s32_7b3750e1:

    # "A shrieking laugh shatters my trance. Whipping round, I find a small building squished between a thrift store and a pawnshop."
    "Una risa estridente rompe mi trance. Al girarme, encuentro un edificio pequeño apretado entre una tienda de segunda mano y una casa de empeño."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:86
translate spanish hwb_s32_dfb0d909:

    # "I pull off to the side and peek in, wanting nothing more than to forget about everything."
    "Me aparto a un lado y me asomo, sin querer nada más que olvidarme de todo."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:88
translate spanish hwb_s32_f12ce092:

    # "It’s smaller than the RV, the entire middle dedicated to four mismatched bars set up in a square, surrounded by cheesy island decor and streamers hanging from the ceiling. Under it all—a legion of girls."
    "Es más pequeño que la casa rodante, con todo el centro dedicado a cuatro barras disparejas colocadas en un cuadrado, rodeadas de decoración isleña cursi y serpentinas colgando del techo. Debajo de todo eso—una legión de chicas."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:90
translate spanish hwb_s32_36d85f01:

    # "Tall girls, girly-girls, redheads, blondes and brunettes, all crammed inside and chatting each other up in a festival of free-flowing drinks."
    "Chicas altas, chicas femeninas, pelirrojas, rubias y morenas, todas apretujadas adentro y coqueteando entre sí en un festival de bebidas a raudales."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:94
translate spanish hwb_s32_3b16d20d:

    # Amber "O-Oh."
    Amber "Огооо."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:96
translate spanish hwb_s32_88261855:

    # "I get to see myself blush in real time thanks to the window. The rest of the bar probably does, too. I must look like an idiot."
    "Puedo verme sonrojar en tiempo real gracias a la ventana. El resto del bar probablemente también lo ve. Debo parecer una idiota."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:100
translate spanish hwb_s32_424515a0:

    # "I don't leave, though."
    "Pero no me voy."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:102
translate spanish hwb_s32_b5255041:

    # "Sitting at the bar beneath the red and pink party lights is a slim girl with shaggy rainbow-dyed hair. She sways on her stool as she laughs with the bartender, the shape of her ass outlined in her tight jeans."
    "Sentada en la barra bajo las luces de fiesta rojas y rosas hay una chica delgada con el pelo teñido de arcoíris despeinado. Se mece en su taburete mientras ríe con el cantinero, la forma de su trasero marcada en sus jeans ajustados."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:104
translate spanish hwb_s32_0d6c6a65:

    # "I can't buy her a drink. But then again, this is the place for it. Maybe I..."
    "No puedo comprarle una copa. Pero, por otro lado, este es el lugar para eso. Tal vez yo..."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:106
translate spanish hwb_s32_218786f2:

    # "Catching a glimpse of me, she turns to the window and gives me a big, bright smile."
    "Al verme, se gira hacia la ventana y me dedica una sonrisa grande y brillante."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:111
translate spanish hwb_s32_0105cc8b:

    # "Images of Marina flash through my head."
    "Imágenes de Marina pasan por mi cabeza."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:113
translate spanish hwb_s32_c89bb407:

    # "Images from last night at first—her holding me, me kissing her neck."
    "Imágenes de anoche al principio—ella abrazándome, yo besando su cuello."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:125
translate spanish hwb_s32_41bc14dc:

    # "And then the Valley of Fire. Finding all the pieces of the treasure. Helping her on the side of the road."
    "Y luego el Valle de Fuego. Encontrando todas las piezas del tesoro. Ayudándola al lado del camino."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:133
translate spanish hwb_s32_cc36dbb4:

    # "But the images that stick out the most are the quiet times. Me driving on the highway while Marina sways back and forth to my music."
    "Pero las imágenes que más resaltan son los momentos tranquilos. Yo conduciendo por la carretera mientras Marina se balancea de un lado a otro con mi música."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:141
translate spanish hwb_s32_c047e48c:

    # "I back away, then take off as fast as I can."
    "Retrocedo, luego salgo corriendo tan rápido como puedo."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:145
translate spanish hwb_s32_c99559eb:

    # "Am I that disgusting? Was that all Marina was to me?"
    "¿Soy tan repugnante? ¿Eso era todo lo que Marina significaba para mí?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:147
translate spanish hwb_s32_41781e51:

    # "I slap myself. When it barely stings, I do it again, smacking myself so hard that tears bead in my eyes. Blinking them back, I swallow, and keep running."
    "Me abofeteo. Cuando apenas duele, lo hago de nuevo, golpeándome tan fuerte que se me forman lágrimas en los ojos. Parpadeando para contenerlas, trago saliva y sigo corriendo."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:153
translate spanish hwb_s32_46a15ebc:

    # "One by one, the shops vanish behind me. The sidewalk thins, then disappears. Eventually, it's too dark to even see the ground, and I'm running under unfiltered starlight."
    "Una por una, las tiendas desaparecen detrás de mí. La acera se estrecha, luego desaparece. Finalmente, está demasiado oscuro para siquiera ver el suelo, y corro bajo la luz de las estrellas sin filtro."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:162
translate spanish hwb_s32_50c9d689:

    # "When I finally stop, my shoes are heavy with sand. I wilt over and suck in huge, gasping breaths."
    "Cuando finalmente me detengo, mis zapatos están pesados de arena. Me doblo y jalo grandes bocanadas de aire."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:164
translate spanish hwb_s32_8bb15166:

    # "Forcing myself to look over my shoulder, I realize I’m surrounded by sand dunes and rocky hill ranges."
    "Forzándome a mirar por encima del hombro, me doy cuenta de que estoy rodeada de dunas de arena y cadenas montañosas rocosas."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:166
translate spanish hwb_s32_b81616d7:

    # "I’ve left the city far behind me. My footprints prove that."
    "He dejado la ciudad muy atrás. Mis huellas lo demuestran."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:168
translate spanish hwb_s32_cdc8967a:

    # "The saguaro cacti are scattered at random, like sorrowful people brooding under the moonlight, their prickly limbs reaching for the sky."
    "Los cactus saguaro están dispersos al azar, como personas apenadas meditando bajo la luz de la luna, sus extremidades espinosas alcanzando el cielo."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:173
translate spanish hwb_s32_3c40b12a:

    # "I settle my breathing and listen to the sounds of the desert."
    "Calmo mi respiración y escucho los sonidos del desierto."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:176
translate spanish hwb_s32_4c5db352:

    # "A gust of wind stirring the dry air. The crackly yelp of a coyote. The whimsical horns and hypnotic guitar strums of faint ska music—{w=0.8}wait."
    "Una ráfaga de viento agitando el aire seco. El aullido chirriante de un coyote. Los cuernos caprichosos y los rasgueos hipnóticos de guitarra de una música ska tenue—{w=0.8}espera."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:179
translate spanish hwb_s32_595c11ae:

    # "Now I really am disgusted."
    "Ahora sí que estoy asqueada."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:182
translate spanish hwb_s32_84dbe378:

    # "Squinting at the horizon, I catch a glimpse of an unmoving light."
    "Entrecerrando los ojos hacia el horizonte, vislumbro una luz inmóvil."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:184
translate spanish hwb_s32_5dc3d0f4:

    # "It’s faint and alone, but it’s definitely there."
    "Es tenue y solitaria, pero definitivamente está ahí."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:188
translate spanish hwb_s32_fed41fcc:

    # "Pressured by some kind of masochism harbored deep within me, I follow the light."
    "Presionada por una especie de masoquismo albergado en lo profundo de mí, sigo la luz."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:190
translate spanish hwb_s32_4905b40a:

    # "The further I get, the more I know I should turn back, but my fears are just proved right as I inch closer."
    "Cuanto más avanzo, más sé que debería regresar, pero mis miedos se confirman a medida que me acerco."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:192
translate spanish hwb_s32_e66544af:

    # "A black motorhome with stripes just as hideous as the music blasting from it."
    "Una casa rodante negra con rayas tan horribles como la música que sale de ella."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:194
translate spanish hwb_s32_3f14a334:

    # "With every screech of a trumpet, my ears bleed a little more. Every time the guitar plays that stupid, unchanging rhythm, I die inside."
    "Con cada chirrido de trompeta, mis sangran un poco más. Cada vez que la guitarra toca ese estúpido e invariable ritmo, muero por dentro."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:196
translate spanish hwb_s32_6f1b44f0:

    # "But the worst part is something I’ve never even been subjected to before."
    "Pero lo peor es algo a lo que nunca antes había estado expuesta."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:198
translate spanish hwb_s32_b60a1a88:

    # "Singing."
    "Cantar."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:200
translate spanish hwb_s32_5b80c7c6:

    # "If you can call it that."
    "Si se le puede llamar así."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:202
translate spanish hwb_s32_0ae00e02:

    # "Not from the song, but from a familiar brain-piercing wail masking over it."
    "No de la canción, sino de un familiar alarido perforador de cerebros que la cubre."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:204
translate spanish hwb_s32_c69e3a48:

    # "It’s awful. Like a dying siren trying to reel in one last sailor."
    "Es horrible. Como una sirena moribunda tratando de atraer a un último marinero."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:206
translate spanish hwb_s32_8eab83bf:

    # "Covering my ears doesn’t help. I can only wince in agony as it reaches a high note, probably killing any wildlife in the general area."
    "Taparme los oídos no ayuda. Solo puedo hacer una mueca de agonía cuando alcanza una nota alta, probablemente matando a cualquier vida silvestre en el área general."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:208
translate spanish hwb_s32_9215ed04:

    # "Someone needs to stop this."
    "Alguien necesita detener esto."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:213
translate spanish hwb_s32_b9bb0a07:

    # "I march to the door, wondering why I’m even going to bother. After everything she’s pulled, why should I when I can just go about my life."
    "Marcho hacia la puerta, preguntándome por qué siquiera me molesto. Después de todo lo que ha hecho, ¿por qué debería hacerlo cuando puedo seguir con mi vida?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:217
translate spanish hwb_s32_cdac2f7b:

    # "But then she reaches the chorus."
    "Pero entonces llega al estribillo."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:221
translate spanish hwb_s32_ca925aac:

    # "Yeah, that’s why."
    "Sí, por eso."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:223
translate spanish hwb_s32_7cf2acf1:

    # "I give the door three solid bangs. The singing stops."
    "Doy tres golpes firmes a la puerta. El canto se detiene."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:238
translate spanish hwb_s32_8ea064a0:

    # Mariah "Hah! I knew you numbskulls couldn’t live without me!"
    Mariah "Хах! Я знала, что вы, тупицы, не можете жить без меня!"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:240
translate spanish hwb_s32_de076d09:

    # "Mariah swings the door open. She’s flushed, dangling a glass bottle from her hand only to be silenced to a single sniff upon seeing me."
    "Mariah abre la puerta de golpe. Está sonrojada, colgando una botella de vidrio de su mano, solo para callarse con un solo sollozo al verme."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:244
translate spanish hwb_s32_0fe2d220:

    # Amber "You suck at treasure hunting {i}and{/i} singing. Go figure."
    Amber "Ты отстойна и в охоте за сокровищами {i}и{/i} в пении. Удивительно."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:253
translate spanish hwb_s32_18e27051:

    # "She slams the door in my face."
    "Me cierra la puerta en la cara."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:269
translate spanish hwb_s32_36a7fb93:

    # "I knock again. It’s delayed, but she reopens the door, her head cautiously peeking halfway out."
    "Toco otra vez. Tarda, pero vuelve a abrir la puerta, asomando la cabeza con cautela a medias."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:271
translate spanish hwb_s32_40e1999f:

    # Mariah "You’ve taken everything from me. What else could you possibly want?"
    Mariah " Ты уже все забрала у меня. Что еще тебе нужно?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:275
translate spanish hwb_s32_29858d1b:

    # Amber "Your soul."
    Amber "Твоя душа."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:280
translate spanish hwb_s32_4b8560f0:

    # Mariah "Give me the treasure and you got a deal. I’ll throw in the slackers, too."
    Mariah "Отдай мне сокровище и разойдемся. Я тебе еще и этих бездельников в придачу отдам."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:284
translate spanish hwb_s32_893b3875:

    # Amber "That’s… Probably not gonna happen."
    Amber "Но это...наверное, это вряд ли возможно."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:286
translate spanish hwb_s32_c4daa19a:

    # "She leans out the door, nearly stumbling over as she peers from side-to-side."
    "Se asoma por la puerta, casi tropezando mientras mira de un lado a otro."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:290
translate spanish hwb_s32_6dc9c96f:

    # Mariah "Where’s your better half?"
    Mariah "Где твоя лучшая половинка?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:292
translate spanish hwb_s32_f68cfca4:

    # "I look down."
    "Bajo la mirada."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:294
translate spanish hwb_s32_87c61fb2:

    # "How do I even answer that?"
    "¿Cómo respondo a eso?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:300
translate spanish hwb_s32_87d03766:

    # "Mariah growls and limps towards her refrigerator."
    "Mariah gruñe y cojea hacia su refrigerador."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:302
translate spanish hwb_s32_be4875f3:

    # Mariah "Come {cps=5}iiiiii{/cps}n."
    Mariah "Вход{cps=5}ииииии/cps}."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:306
translate spanish hwb_s32_fc674fa2:

    # "May as well. No one is waiting for me anymore, and yelling at Mariah is as good of a distraction as any."
    "Total, por qué no. Ya nadie me espera, y gritarle a Mariah es una distracción tan buena como cualquier otra."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:312
translate spanish hwb_s32_faa723b0:

    # "I climb in. My nose is instantly assaulted with the smell of rancid beer."
    "Entro. Mi nariz es instantáneamente atacada por el olor a cerveza rancia."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:314
translate spanish hwb_s32_6f091856:

    # "And whisky."
    "Y whisky."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:316
translate spanish hwb_s32_a3f087fb:

    # "And vodka."
    "Y vodka."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:318
translate spanish hwb_s32_de673a61:

    # "There might even be traces of a skunk."
    "Hasta podría haber rastros de un zorrillo."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:320
translate spanish hwb_s32_91ac28fb:

    # "I decide to breathe through my mouth."
    "Decido respirar por la boca."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:322
translate spanish hwb_s32_2103a2b8:

    # "The couch and cot are both empty. No lackies to feed into Mariah’s delusions in sight."
    "El sofá y el catre están vacíos. Ni rastro de secuaces que alimenten las ilusiones de Mariah."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:326
translate spanish hwb_s32_67b99a9f:

    # Amber "Where are the other two?"
    Amber "А где еще двое?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:328
translate spanish hwb_s32_ebdca702:

    # "Head in the depths of her fridge, Mariah only snorts."
    "Con la cabeza metida en el fondo del refrigerador, Mariah solo resopla."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:330
translate spanish hwb_s32_0e10e6ed:

    # Mariah "Tess wanted to see some stupid walk of fame, so Joe took her."
    Mariah "Тесс хотела посмотреть на какую то идиотскую тропу славы, так что Джо повел ее туда."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:334
translate spanish hwb_s32_73dab1f8:

    # Amber "Palm Springs has a walk of fame?"
    Amber "В Палм Спрингс есть тропа славы?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:336
translate spanish hwb_s32_a3edeea5:

    # Mariah "According to the squirt."
    Mariah "Согласно словам этой выскочки - да."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:341
translate spanish hwb_s32_a33ae682:

    # "She leans back out of the fridge."
    "Se inclina hacia atrás, saliendo del refrigerador."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:343
translate spanish hwb_s32_75a17f5d:

    # Mariah "How old are you?"
    Mariah "Так сколько тебе лет?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:347
translate spanish hwb_s32_4490c4b7:

    # Amber "Nineteen. Why?"
    Amber "Девятнадцать, а что?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:349
translate spanish hwb_s32_f2c82acb:

    # Mariah "Close enough. Drink."
    Mariah "Почти хватает. Пей."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:351
translate spanish hwb_s32_026ce932:

    # "With a loose throw that I actually have to dive for, she tosses me a bottle."
    "Con un lanzamiento flojo que de verdad tengo que esquivar, me tira una botella."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:353
translate spanish hwb_s32_1e68cd56:

    # "The print is in Spanish, carved into the thick glass just above the label."
    "La inscripción está en español, tallada en el vidrio grueso justo encima de la etiqueta."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:355
translate spanish hwb_s32_9a3ecfbe:

    # "I try pronouncing it, but it comes out sounding depressingly American."
    "Intento pronunciarlo, pero suena deprimentemente estadounidense."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:359
translate spanish hwb_s32_e175ebb4:

    # Mariah "You should be worshipping me. That’s the good stuff."
    Mariah "Не слышу оваций. Эта вещь очень хороша."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:363
translate spanish hwb_s32_7efbe430:

    # Amber "I’m ecstatic."
    Amber "Я в восторге."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:365
translate spanish hwb_s32_20e360ad:

    # "I think she’s too far gone to notice the flatness in my voice. Even if she did, I doubt she’d care, with something resembling happiness on her face as she cradles half a dozen or so bottles to the couch."
    "Creo que está demasiado ida para notar la monotonía en mi voz. Incluso si lo hiciera, dudo que le importara, con algo parecido a la felicidad en su rostro mientras acuna media docena de botellas hacia el sofá."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:369
translate spanish hwb_s32_60366135:

    # Amber "You gonna drink all that? Haven’t you had enough?"
    Amber "Ты собираешься выпить все это? Разве тебе уже не хватит?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:373
translate spanish hwb_s32_550bc701:

    # Mariah "Go die. You stole my equipment and my treasure. I’m not letting you steal my forty ounces to freedom."
    Mariah "Убейся. Ты украла мое снаряжение и сокровище. Я не дам тебе украсть мой последний оплот свободы."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:391
translate spanish hwb_s32_cfe55bee:

    # "I shrug and flop down beside her. Mariah drunkenly reaches for the remote, misses it twice, then switches off the music and hurls the remote across the room."
    "Me encojo de hombros y me dejo caer a su lado. Mariah, borracha, estira la mano hacia el control remoto, lo falla dos veces, luego apaga la música y lanza el control al otro lado de la habitación."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:393
translate spanish hwb_s32_03982125:

    # Amber "Finally, thank you! I hate ska!"
    Amber "Наконец то, спасибо! Я ненавижу ска."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:395
translate spanish hwb_s32_881b8021:

    # "Mariah snarls at me like a toothless piranha."
    "Mariah me gruñe como una piraña sin dientes."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:399
translate spanish hwb_s32_88f14c8d:

    # Mariah "It’s reggae, you uncultured brat!"
    Mariah "Это рэгги, бескультурная малявка!"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:401
translate spanish hwb_s32_bdec2fc7:

    # "She slumps back down."
    "Se deja caer hacia atrás."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:403
translate spanish hwb_s32_8eefbc2b:

    # Mariah "But ska’s okay too."
    Mariah "Но и ска тоже хорош."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:405
translate spanish hwb_s32_474c7a55:

    # Amber "Uncultured?"
    Amber "Бескультурная?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:407
translate spanish hwb_s32_603d2c11:

    # Amber "You were the one who wanted to blow up Shiprock!"
    Amber "Это же ты хотела взорвать “Шипрок”!"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:409
translate spanish hwb_s32_ca07647f:

    # Mariah "It was a suggestion—a suggestion!"
    Mariah "Это было просто предложение - пре-дло-же-ние."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:411
translate spanish hwb_s32_1a9a2227:

    # Mariah "I don’t have nearly enough TNT for that."
    Mariah "И у меня даже нет такого количества динамита."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:413
translate spanish hwb_s32_76a0e156:

    # Amber "The fact that you even have it is what bothers me."
    Amber "Тот факт, что он вообще у тебя есть - уже повод для беспокойства."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:415
translate spanish hwb_s32_cafdd5fd:

    # Mariah "Whatever, at least I know what I listen to is good, unlike whatever you’re into."
    Mariah "Но как бы там ни было, я хотя бы разбираюсь в музыке, в отличии от тебя."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:420
translate spanish hwb_s32_d69db84c:

    # Amber "Oh, I can assure you what I listen to is better than ska."
    Amber "Ну, я могу тебя заверить, что слушаю музыку намного лучше, чем ска."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:424
translate spanish hwb_s32_e981de04:

    # Mariah "Reggae!"
    Mariah "Рэгги!"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:426
translate spanish hwb_s32_470dd5d8:

    # Amber "Jazz fusion, new-age, world music. All better than your circus noise."
    Amber "Джаз-фьюжн, нью-эйдж, этническая музыка. Все это лучше, чем эти твои цирковые шумы."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:428
translate spanish hwb_s32_a54e0699:

    # Mariah "You actually like that hippie-dippie crap? What Volkswagen did you fall out of?"
    Mariah "Тебе и правда нравиться это хиппи-шмиппи дерьмо? Из какого Фольксвагена ты выпала?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:430
translate spanish hwb_s32_fc7acd59:

    # Amber "The one that hit your mother when she was pregnant with you, apparently."
    Amber "Судя по всему из того, который ударил твою мать, когда она была беременна."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:434
translate spanish hwb_s32_6197117f:

    # "We both click our tongues. Without looking, she pops my cap with a bottle opener, then hers. Giving a half-assed clink of our bottles, we take a swig."
    "Ambas chasqueamos la lengua. Sin mirar, me destapa la botella con un abridor, luego la suya. Con un tintineo a medias de nuestras botellas, damos un trago."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:436
translate spanish hwb_s32_f1aa522e:

    # "The swampy drink tails down my throat, setting my chest on fire."
    "El líquido pantanoso baja por mi garganta, incendiándome el pecho."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:438
translate spanish hwb_s32_d41d56f4:

    # "My experience with alcohol is really limited. Gramps didn’t keep a lot of booze around, and when he did it was always mead or wine."
    "Mi experiencia con el alcohol es muy limitada. El abuelo no tenía muchas bebidas alcohólicas por aquí, y cuando las tenía, siempre era hidromiel o vino."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:440
translate spanish hwb_s32_776ebc68:

    # "I only snuck some out a few times for ‘special’ dates."
    "Solo saqué algunas a escondidas un par de veces para citas 'especiales'."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:442
translate spanish hwb_s32_6807428e:

    # Mariah "Gotta say, you’re a lot less bearable without the ditz holding you on a leash."
    Mariah "Хочу сказать, что ты более невыносима без той стукнутой, которая держала тебя на поводке."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:444
translate spanish hwb_s32_74e51c34:

    # Amber "Shut up!"
    Amber "Заткнись!"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:446
translate spanish hwb_s32_92d7fbf8:

    # "She barely held the flame to the fuse, but that single word is enough to make something inside of me go off."
    "Apenas sostuvo la llama contra la mecha, pero esa única palabra es suficiente para que algo dentro de mí estalle."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:451
translate spanish hwb_s32_ac15ea64:

    # Amber "Don’t you talk about her that way! She’s a kinder, more caring person than you’ll ever be!"
    Amber "Не смей так говорить о ней! Она заботливее и добрее, чем ты когда-либо будешь!"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:453
translate spanish hwb_s32_48fcf022:

    # "Mariah scrunches her nose, like my outburst didn’t make any sense to her dumb, drunk face."
    "Mariah arruga la nariz, como si mi arrebato no tuviera sentido para su estúpida cara borracha."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:458
translate spanish hwb_s32_260ce986:

    # Mariah "That’s not a very high bar."
    Mariah "Не очень то высокую планку задаешь."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:462
translate spanish hwb_s32_16c66a19:

    # "She’s not wrong, but couldn’t she have at least {i}tried{/i} defending herself?"
    "No está equivocada, pero ¿no podría al menos {i}haber{/i} intentado defenderse?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:464
translate spanish hwb_s32_4a0cf4c2:

    # "I groan and let my blood simmer down, but not before spitting out one more shot of venom."
    "Gimo y dejo que mi sangre se enfríe, pero no sin antes escupir un último dardo de veneno."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:467
translate spanish hwb_s32_279b6bd5:

    # Amber "Whatever. It’s not like you’re any better. You’re a mess without the other two keeping you in check."
    Amber "Как бы то ни было, ты ничем не лучше. Если бы не эти двое, что держат тебя под контролем, ты бы устроила хаос."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:469
translate spanish hwb_s32_7eba9851:

    # Mariah "Hey! Don’t get any ideas! I’m the one keeping {i}them{/i} in check."
    Mariah "Эй! Не придумывай там! Это я держу {i}этих двоих{/i} под контролем."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:471
translate spanish hwb_s32_c3b81394:

    # Mariah "They’d be dead by now if it weren’t for me."
    Mariah "Они бы уже давно отъехали, если бы не я."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:473
translate spanish hwb_s32_a75b99d1:

    # "Sure, Mariah."
    "Claro, Mariah."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:475
translate spanish hwb_s32_f9769244:

    # "I pinch the bridge of my nose and shake my head with a short laugh."
    "Me pellizco el puente de la nariz y niego con la cabeza con una risa breve."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:477
translate spanish hwb_s32_8ce91be4:

    # "Whether or not I choose to accept that Mariah exists in my reality, she’s at least something familiar. ‘Comforting’ probably isn’t the right word for it, but she’s someone to talk to."
    "Ya sea que elija aceptar o no que Mariah existe en mi realidad, al menos es algo familiar. 'Reconfortante' probablemente no sea la palabra correcta, pero es alguien con quien hablar."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:479
translate spanish hwb_s32_8200bcc4:

    # Amber "Why are you here, anyway?"
    Amber "И все таки, почему ты здесь?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:481
translate spanish hwb_s32_db73c62f:

    # Mariah "Who even knows?"
    Mariah "А кто знает?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:483
translate spanish hwb_s32_255fefe5:

    # Mariah "Joe mentioned something about a music orgy thing."
    Mariah "Джо говорил что-то о музыкальной оргии."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:485
translate spanish hwb_s32_9d260bdd:

    # Amber "‘Music orgy?’ You mean the festival?"
    Amber "“Музыкальная оргия?” Ты про фестиваль?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:487
translate spanish hwb_s32_4ab4bb6f:

    # Mariah "Yeah, that."
    Mariah "Да, о нем."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:489
translate spanish hwb_s32_df869483:

    # Amber "Huh. And you went along with it? I guess that makes sense. You guys are a thing, right?"
    Amber "Хах. И ты согласилась? Хотя это имеет смысл. Между вами что-то есть, так?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:491
translate spanish hwb_s32_79251bfa:

    # "Building up from a bunch of snorts, Mariah bursts out laughing."
    "Empezando con una serie de resoplidos, Mariah estalla en carcajadas."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:493
translate spanish hwb_s32_e36b3b7d:

    # Mariah "Hah! Me and that slacker wouldn’t be a thing if the planets collided, wiped out everything, formed a mega-planet and we had to repopulate."
    Mariah "Ахаха! У меня с этим бездельником ничего не было бы, даже если бы планеты столкнулись, образовали мега-планету, убив все живое в процессе, а нам надо было ее заново заселить.  "

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:495
translate spanish hwb_s32_137cb6ec:

    # "Why do I get the feeling this exact scenario has been played out in her journal multiple times?"
    "¿Por qué tengo la sensación de que esta escena exacta se ha repetido varias veces en su diario?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:497
translate spanish hwb_s32_87dfc70b:

    # Mariah "Besides, there’s more important things to focus on."
    Mariah "Тем более, есть много вещей поважнее, на которых стоит сфокусироваться."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:499
translate spanish hwb_s32_50c22065:

    # Mariah "Or, at least…"
    Mariah "Ну, или по крайней мере…"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:501
translate spanish hwb_s32_56380786:

    # "She looks at the drawer again then glares at me."
    "Vuelve a mirar el cajón y luego me fulmina con la mirada."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:503
translate spanish hwb_s32_dca44d88:

    # Mariah "There were."
    Mariah "Были."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:505
translate spanish hwb_s32_6847d622:

    # "I hide the temptation to laugh in her face and take another gulp."
    "Escondo las ganas de reírme en su cara y doy otro trago."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:507
translate spanish hwb_s32_4653b51a:

    # Amber "So nothing, huh? You grow up with someone and don’t feel the tiniest thing for them?"
    Amber "Значит ничего, да? Ты выросла вместе с ним, но совсем ничего к нему не чувствуешь?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:509
translate spanish hwb_s32_0d15f4f4:

    # Mariah "Eh."
    Mariah "Мэ."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:511
translate spanish hwb_s32_054894d6:

    # "She takes another swig, but this time just gives the wall a dry, blank stare."
    "Ella da otro trago, pero esta vez solo se queda mirando la pared con una mirada vacía y seca."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:513
translate spanish hwb_s32_7844e115:

    # Mariah "If he’s still single in ten years, {i}maybe{/i} I’ll marry him out of pity."
    Mariah "Если он будет одинок еще лет десять,  то {i}может быть{/i} я выйду за него из жалости."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:515
translate spanish hwb_s32_abe42c1d:

    # "I bet she’d marry the treasure in a heartbeat, though. Probably do more than just marry it."
    "Apuesto a que se casaría con el tesoro en un santiamén. Probablemente haría más que solo casarse con él."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:517
translate spanish hwb_s32_40b0c0b2:

    # Mariah "What about you and the ditz? Aren’t you two going to the music orgy together?"
    Mariah "А что на счет тебя и этой? Разве вы не ехали на музыкальную оргию вместе?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:519
translate spanish hwb_s32_5d39db5f:

    # "Her eyes narrow."
    "Sus ojos se entrecierran."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:521
translate spanish hwb_s32_a7d22096:

    # Mariah "I’ll kill you if that’s what you’re using my treasure for, by the way."
    Mariah "Кстати, я убью тебя, если это то, на что вы тратите мое сокровище."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:523
translate spanish hwb_s32_4a5d4966:

    # "I don’t answer, looking at my now near-empty bottle instead."
    "No respondo, mirando en cambio mi botella casi vacía."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:525
translate spanish hwb_s32_deb5c927:

    # Mariah "What? You two have a fight?"
    Mariah "Что? Вы сильно повздорили?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:527
translate spanish hwb_s32_226084ea:

    # Amber "Something like that."
    Amber "Вроде того."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:529
translate spanish hwb_s32_115a9abc:

    # Mariah "I bet it was because of the gold. No honor among thieves, I tell ya."
    Mariah "Держу пари, что это из-за золота. Нет чести среди воров, так я говорю."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:531
translate spanish hwb_s32_277e467e:

    # Amber "No. Nothing like that."
    Amber "Нет. Не из за этого."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:533
translate spanish hwb_s32_60d46e7f:

    # Amber "It’s… It’s hard to explain."
    Amber "Это… Это трудно объяснить."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:535
translate spanish hwb_s32_586932dc:

    # Mariah "Well, I don’t really care, but go ahead and moan, if you want. It’s not any different than what you usually do."
    Mariah "Ну, мне на самом деле, насрать. Ты можешь продолжать свои жалобы и стоны, как ты обычно и делаешь."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:539
translate spanish hwb_s32_85d67ea4:

    # "I look at Mariah. She doesn’t seem particularly invested, interested in downing more beers than anything."
    "Miro a Mariah. No parece particularmente interesada, más que nada en beber más cervezas."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:541
translate spanish hwb_s32_7175e9a7:

    # "She’s a maniac, that has always been, and still is, abundantly clear. She probably {i}would{/i} tear apart the entire Southwest if left unattended. Hell, maybe even the entire nation."
    "Es una maníaca, eso siempre ha sido, y sigue siendo, abundantemente claro. Probablemente {i}sí{/i} destrozaría todo el Suroeste si la dejaran sola. Demonios, tal vez incluso toda la nación."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:543
translate spanish hwb_s32_246e74bd:

    # "She’s no Joe. No way she could hold up an actual conversation. No way she could accidentally offer some good advice. No way she feels any sympathy."
    "No es como Joe. De ninguna manera podría mantener una conversación real. De ninguna manera podría dar algún consejo útil por accidente. De ninguna manera siente alguna simpatía."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:545
translate spanish hwb_s32_b1cfc49b:

    # "Still, I feel like I can vent to her."
    "Aun así, siento que puedo desahogarme con ella."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:547
translate spanish hwb_s32_49915be8:

    # "Not trust her. Not after all the RV chases and games of blackjack. But vent."
    "No confiar en ella. No después de todas las persecuciones en casa rodante y partidas de blackjack. Pero desahogarme."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:549
translate spanish hwb_s32_b39d4a4c:

    # "She doesn’t care, but maybe that’s what makes it so appealing."
    "No le importa, pero quizás eso es lo que lo hace tan atractivo."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:551
translate spanish hwb_s32_c9e845f6:

    # "I stay silent and stare at the ceiling, mulling over everything that’s happened, searching for the right words, words I couldn’t even give to Marina."
    "Me quedo en silencio y miro al techo, reflexionando sobre todo lo que ha pasado, buscando las palabras correctas, palabras que ni siquiera pude darle a Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:553
translate spanish hwb_s32_40c09524:

    # Mariah "I said that I don’t care, not that I’m willing to wait all night so you can steal my time too."
    Mariah "Я сказала, что мне наплевать, а не то, что я готова ждать всю ночь и ты можешь занять все мое время."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:555
translate spanish hwb_s32_5a7ca1c7:

    # Amber "Just give me a minute! I’m not really used to… this."
    Amber "Просто дай мне минуту! Я не привыкла к... подобному."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:588
translate spanish hwb_s32_88b76a4e:

    # "Taking a deep breath, I look past Mariah, unwilling to let her see my shame."
    "Tomando un respiro profundo, miro más allá de Mariah, sin querer que vea mi vergüenza."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:590
translate spanish hwb_s32_c444fdcb:

    # "The single shred of pride I have left snaps and I let all the weakness come fumbling out."
    "El único jirón de orgullo que me queda se rompe y dejo que toda la debilidad salga a trompicones."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:596
translate spanish hwb_s32_44930194:

    # Amber "I met Marina a little after my grandpa died."
    Amber "Я встретила Марину спустя немного времени после смерти моего дедушки."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:601
translate spanish hwb_s32_c82de6d1:

    # Amber "He was…"
    Amber "Он был…"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:603
translate spanish hwb_s32_3c16ea35:

    # "My chest tightens."
    "El pecho se me aprieta."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:607
translate spanish hwb_s32_18fc59aa:

    # Amber "He was my best friend."
    Amber "Он был моим лучшим другом."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:609
translate spanish hwb_s32_49b3eb8a:

    # Amber "My parents didn’t want me, but he did."
    Amber "Мои родители не хотели меня, но не он."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:611
translate spanish hwb_s32_803142a6:

    # Amber "He raised me in that motorhome. He didn’t have to, but he took care of me anyway."
    Amber "Он дал мне этот трейлер. Он не должен был, но все равно заботился обо мне."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:613
translate spanish hwb_s32_f83d6dc2:

    # "Mariah sips at her beer, listening in silence. No smarmy remarks or deluded rambling."
    "Mariah bebe su cerveza a sorbos, escuchando en silencio. Sin comentarios sarcásticos ni divagaciones delirantes."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:615
translate spanish hwb_s32_a26b92c3:

    # Amber "So when I was a kid, I decided I was gonna take care of him too. Gratitude, y’know?"
    Amber "Так что, когда я была ребенком, то решила, что буду тоже заботиться о нем. Ну знаешь, в качестве благодарности?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:622
translate spanish hwb_s32_7c0959c7:

    # Amber "Gratitude for a lot of things."
    Amber "Благодарности за столько всего..."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:624
translate spanish hwb_s32_c32aced2:

    # Amber "His love. {w=0.7}His acceptance. {w=0.7}The music."
    Amber "За его любовь. {w=0.7}Его понимание. {w=0.7}Музыку."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:628
translate spanish hwb_s32_654c327e:

    # "I stifle a laugh."
    "Contengo una risa."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:630
translate spanish hwb_s32_dca711d3:

    # Amber "God, the music."
    Amber "О боже, музыка."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:632
translate spanish hwb_s32_582e151f:

    # Amber "The goof could spout random trivia about the weirdest music—bands you’ve never even heard of."
    Amber "Я слушала такие разные музыкальные группы, о которых ты даже и не слышала."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:634
translate spanish hwb_s32_93689456:

    # Amber "But I loved it. And I loved him."
    Amber "Я обожала это. И я обожала его."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:636
translate spanish hwb_s32_b8ca44df:

    # Amber "It sounds dumb. A little girl feeling responsible for some full-grown geezer."
    Amber "Это звучит глупо. Маленькая девочка чувствовала себя ответственной за старого чудика."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:638
translate spanish hwb_s32_2839d000:

    # Amber "I didn’t care, though. I wanted to prove how much he meant to me."
    Amber "Но мне было все равно. Я просто хотела показать, как много он значит для меня."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:640
translate spanish hwb_s32_d0903eb3:

    # Amber "And that’s how it worked for the longest time."
    Amber "И вот так все было очень долгое время."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:644
translate spanish hwb_s32_c696815b:

    # Amber "But then he got sick."
    Amber "Но потом он заболел."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:646
translate spanish hwb_s32_3eda9095:

    # "I funnel down the beer and reach for another one. Mariah shoves her hand in front of me and pops off the cap, right as the next cycle of heartbreak starts closing in."
    "Me tomo la cerveza de un trago y busco otra. Mariah mete la mano frente a mí y quita la tapa justo cuando el siguiente ciclo de angustia empieza a cerrarse."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:648
translate spanish hwb_s32_362bb1f9:

    # "I whisk back the bottle and force it down. Soapy foam rushes to the top and spills over as I pull it back. Mariah only shrugs."
    "Retiro la botella de un tirón y la fuerzo hacia abajo. Espuma jabonosa sube hasta arriba y se derrama cuando la aparto. Mariah solo se encoge de hombros."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:650
translate spanish hwb_s32_b4a20c47:

    # Amber "That festival? He was the one who bought those tickets. It was gonna be {i}our{/i} trip."
    Amber "А фестиваль... Дедушка купил на него билеты. Это должно было быть {i}наше{/i} путешествие."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:652
translate spanish hwb_s32_d96f3054:

    # Amber "That… didn’t happen."
    Amber "Этого... не случилось."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:654
translate spanish hwb_s32_01ef4d3b:

    # Amber "I failed at my job, but I could at least take the trip for him and try to make up for it."
    Amber "Я даже бросила работу, что поехать в это путешествие ради него."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:660
translate spanish hwb_s32_d8bee7c9:

    # Amber "Then I met Marina."
    Amber "А затем я встретила Марину."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:664
translate spanish hwb_s32_9f50d159:

    # "A smile slips onto my face. Despite everything, even just saying her name makes me feel cheerful."
    "Una sonrisa se me escapa en el rostro. A pesar de todo, solo decir su nombre me hace sentir alegre."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:666
translate spanish hwb_s32_7858a30a:

    # Amber "She was really cute and needed a ride, not to mention oblivious. Maybe it was just instinct, but I wasn’t gonna let someone so innocent fend for themselves in the desert."
    Amber "Она была очень милой, рассеянной и ей очень нужен был кто-то, кто ее подвезет. Может это было просто инстинктивно, но я не могла позволить кому-то столь невинному находиться одному в пустыне."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:670
translate spanish hwb_s32_a2d0b582:

    # Amber "I didn’t plan on sticking around for long, but when we found the first part of the treasure, I… I don’t know. "
    Amber "Я не планировала зависнуть с ней, но мы нашли первую часть сокровища, и... я не знаю. "

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:672
translate spanish hwb_s32_2c8d9cd4:

    # Amber "I told myself I was gonna stick with her because I had to pay off Gramps’ hospital bills and funeral."
    Amber "Я говорила себе, что должна быть с ней, чтобы получить возможность оплатить счета за больницу и похороны дедушки."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:674
translate spanish hwb_s32_abd83ced:

    # Amber "But the truth is, I stuck with her because I felt like it was a second chance."
    Amber "Но правда в том, что я чувствовала, что должна быть с ней, потому что это как будто бы второй шанс."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:676
translate spanish hwb_s32_01fbfc47:

    # Amber "I could do some good. Help and protect someone who really needed it."
    Amber "Я хотела сделать все правильно. Помочь и защитить того, кто реально нуждается в этом."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:678
translate spanish hwb_s32_f7e336fb:

    # Amber "And the closer I got with Marina, the more I felt like she was my responsibility."
    Amber "И чем ближе я была к ней, тем больше чувствовала свою ответственность."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:680
translate spanish hwb_s32_ad090401:

    # Amber "But even more than that, when I was with her…"
    Amber "Даже более того, когда я была с ней..."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:684
translate spanish hwb_s32_a0d90b8e:

    # "My voice cracks, trembling under the weight of my words."
    "Mi voz se quiebra, temblando bajo el peso de mis palabras."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:686
translate spanish hwb_s32_a7854084:

    # Amber "I was happy."
    Amber "Я была счастлива."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:688
translate spanish hwb_s32_497c763d:

    # Amber "It was like Gramps was never even gone—then I remembered he was and I completely shut down. Marina tried comforting me, but I just took advantage of her."
    Amber "Будто бы дедушка и не покидал меня вовсе — затем я вспоминала, что его нет и полностью закрывалась. Марина пыталась утешить меня, но я лишь использовала ее."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:690
translate spanish hwb_s32_17c508dc:

    # Amber "When I woke up, I realized that’s what I’d been doing this entire time."
    Amber "Когда я очнулась, то поняла, что делала это на протяжении всего времени."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:692
translate spanish hwb_s32_84de2105:

    # Amber "I was never protecting her. I was just using her to cope with Gramps."
    Amber "Я никогда не защищала ее, я просто использовала ее, что бы справится с утратой дедушки."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:694
translate spanish hwb_s32_22cb05ec:

    # Amber "So I bought her a ticket home."
    Amber "Я купила ей билет домой."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:696
translate spanish hwb_s32_dae387c2:

    # Amber "She yelled and cried, but I did it anyway."
    Amber "Она кричала и плакала, но я все равно сделала это."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:698
translate spanish hwb_s32_6f2a9db3:

    # Amber "I didn’t just fail Gramps, I made this trip about me, and I hurt Marina."
    Amber "Я не просто предала дедушку. Я сделала это путешествие своим, а не нашим и, к тому же, причинила боль Марине."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:700
translate spanish hwb_s32_0226100a:

    # Amber "I don’t deserve to be happy, and I don’t deserve her."
    Amber "Я не заслуживаю счастья, и я не заслуживаю ее."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:705
translate spanish hwb_s32_cd8757bb:

    # "Soaking in the silence, I blink away an annoying watery speck in my eye and fight back a few sniffles."
    "Sumergida en el silencio, parpadeo para apartar una molesta motita acuosa en el ojo y contengo unos cuantos sollozos."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:710
translate spanish hwb_s32_cf792de9:

    # Mariah "You done?"
    Mariah "Ты закончила?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:714
translate spanish hwb_s32_defadd0a:

    # Amber "Yeah."
    Amber "Да."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:718
translate spanish hwb_s32_ac70eca1:

    # "Mariah polishes off the rest of her drink and slams it down, rattling the other empty bottles on the table."
    "Mariah se termina el resto de su bebida y la golpea contra la mesa, haciendo tintinear las otras botellas vacías."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:720
translate spanish hwb_s32_7791a97c:

    # "Smacking her lips, she stretches her neck. Each bone cracks one after the other, sounding off in a delayed trail."
    "Chasqueando los labios, estira el cuello. Cada hueso cruje uno tras otro, sonando en una estela retardada."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:722
translate spanish hwb_s32_0f2b8c6d:

    # "Then, she turns to me and speaks."
    "Luego, se vuelve hacia mí y habla."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:726
translate spanish hwb_s32_ca5884f0:

    # Mariah "You’re a dumbass."
    Mariah "Ты отбитая дура."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:728
translate spanish hwb_s32_17799653:

    # "I pause."
    "Hago una pausa."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:732
translate spanish hwb_s32_39bfc536:

    # Amber "Excuse me?"
    Amber "Прости?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:737
translate spanish hwb_s32_33751075:

    # Mariah "You heard me!"
    Mariah "Ты меня слышала!"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:743
translate spanish hwb_s32_bd3a3485:

    # "Mariah launches herself at me. I wince as her breath streaks out. The smell was bad before, but now it’s like she rinsed her mouth with whisky."
    "Mariah se lanza hacia mí. Me estremezco cuando su aliento se escapa. El olor ya era malo antes, pero ahora es como si se hubiera enjuagado la boca con whisky."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:745
translate spanish hwb_s32_8ed45bb5:

    # Mariah "God, you piss me off."
    Mariah "Боже, ты бесишь меня."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:747
translate spanish hwb_s32_a963a06c:

    # "A growl emerges from deep within her throat as she looks me over. Then, as if acting on simple instinctive desire, she delivers a stiff smack to the back of my head."
    "Un gruñido emerge desde lo profundo de su garganta mientras me examina. Luego, como actuando por un simple deseo instintivo, me da un golpe seco en la nuca."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:757
translate spanish hwb_s32_88637d64:

    # "For a split second, everything is a fuzzy white. The infuriating image of a snarling Mariah greets me as my vision fades back, partnered with an even more infuriating throbbing."
    "Por un instante, todo es un borrón blanco y difuso. La irritante imagen de una Mariah gruñona me recibe cuando mi visión regresa, acompañada de un latido aún más irritante."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:759
translate spanish hwb_s32_fe570872:

    # Amber "OW! WHAT THE HELL?"
    Amber "АЙ! ЧТО ЗА ЧЕРТ?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:761
translate spanish hwb_s32_d019bcde:

    # Amber "Why are you hitting me? I just spilled my guts to your jerka—"
    Amber "Почему ты бьешь меня? Я же только что тебе свое нутро отк—"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:767
translate spanish hwb_s32_d325e440:

    # Mariah "Shut up, I’m talking now."
    Mariah "Заткнись, я буду говорить."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:774
translate spanish hwb_s32_51b8edb9:

    # "Mariah stumbles off the couch, gripping the table for support. Her face has darkened by several shades of red since I’ve gotten here."
    "Mariah se tambalea del sofá, agarrándose a la mesa para apoyarse. Su rostro se ha oscurecido varios tonos de rojo desde que llegué."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:778
translate spanish hwb_s32_de207143:

    # Mariah "Listen here, thief! Dead is dead is dead!"
    Mariah "Слушай сюда, воровка! Мертвец умер и мертв!"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:780
translate spanish hwb_s32_246a4a6d:

    # Mariah "Your dear old grandad ain’t crying up in Heaven because you decided to do some broad in the back of his RV!"
    Mariah "Твой дедушка не плачет на небе, из за того, что развлекалась в его трейлере!"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:782
translate spanish hwb_s32_2724553a:

    # "Her words burn, right to their fiery core. I can’t believe I ever thought I could count on {i}Mariah{/i}."
    "Sus palabras queman, hasta su núcleo ardiente. No puedo creer que alguna vez pensara que podía contar con {i}Mariah{/i}."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:786
translate spanish hwb_s32_8af9afba:

    # Amber "Where do you even get off sayin—"
    Amber "Почему ты говоришь все эт—"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:792
translate spanish hwb_s32_1445caed:

    # Mariah "I said shut up."
    Mariah "Я сказала заткнись."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:796
translate spanish hwb_s32_a071d5e5:

    # Mariah "Get over your snoozefest of a sob story."
    Mariah "Сколько можно выжимать сопли из этой грустненькой истории."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:798
translate spanish hwb_s32_d9a71c63:

    # Mariah "You got the girl and you got {i}MY{/i} treasure!"
    Mariah "Ты заполучила девчонку, и ты заполучила {i}МОЕ{/i} сокровище!"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:807
translate spanish hwb_s32_5285d0b6:

    # Mariah "But noooooooooo. You can’t be happy because of some stupid, phony sense of obligation!"
    Mariah "Но неееееееееет. Ты не можешь быть счастлива из за какого-то глупого, фальшивого чувства долга!"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:809
translate spanish hwb_s32_02a27cb4:

    # Mariah "AND THAT’S ANOTHER THING!"
    Mariah "И ЕСТЬ ЕЩЕ ОДНО!"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:813
translate spanish hwb_s32_857d92e4:

    # "Her voice gets louder as her words get sloppier, slipping and sliding over each other."
    "Su voz se vuelve más fuerte mientras sus palabras se vuelven más torpes, resbalando y deslizándose unas sobre otras."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:815
translate spanish hwb_s32_cfbbd417:

    # "I couldn’t get a word in even if I tried. All I can do is listen stone-faced as the lashings keep on coming."
    "No podría meter ni una palabra aunque lo intentara. Todo lo que puedo hacer es escuchar con cara de piedra mientras los azotes siguen llegando."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:819
translate spanish hwb_s32_c2875b2f:

    # Mariah "Who the hell do you think you are? What gives you the right to be some self-righteous guardian?"
    Mariah "Кем ты, мать твою, себя возомнила? Кто дал тебе право быть каким-то самодовольным защитником?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:823
translate spanish hwb_s32_2d3057df:

    # Mariah "You don’t look after people because you have to prove yourself! You do it because…"
    Mariah "Ты не заботишься о людях просто потому, чтобы что-то себе доказать! Ты делаешь это потому..."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:828
translate spanish hwb_s32_beb4c3c6:

    # "She stops and scratches her head. I lean in, my breath frozen by anticipation as she tries to decode her own logic."
    "Se detiene y se rasca la cabeza. Me inclino, con la respiración congelada por la anticipación, mientras intenta descifrar su propia lógica."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:830
translate spanish hwb_s32_0ff8f0a3:

    # Mariah "Because you just do! Okay?"
    Mariah "Потому что ты просто делаешь! Уяснила?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:834
translate spanish hwb_s32_496e699a:

    # Mariah "I swear, that annoying complex of yours is gonna smother you and everyone else."
    Mariah "Клянусь, этот твой дебильный комплекс рано или поздно прикончит тебя и всех вокруг тебя."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:836
translate spanish hwb_s32_d5118d16:

    # "Mariah grabs another bottle and swings it straight down on the sharp corner of the table. The cap somersaults through the air. By the time it lands, she’s already chugged most of it."
    "Mariah agarra otra botella y la golpea directamente contra la esquina afilada de la mesa. La tapa da una voltereta en el aire. Para cuando aterriza, ella ya se ha bebido casi toda."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:840
translate spanish hwb_s32_8dd05b05:

    # Amber "But I used her…"
    Amber "Но я же использовала ее…"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:842
translate spanish hwb_s32_7722fa18:

    # "That’s right. Obligations, second chances, complexes. None of that means anything, because it’s all said and done, I used Marina to make myself happy."
    "Así es. Obligaciones, segundas oportunidades, complejos. Nada de eso importa, porque al final, usé a Marina para hacerme feliz."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:846
translate spanish hwb_s32_c702a433:

    # Mariah "You call {i}that{/i} using? Gimme’ a break!"
    Mariah "И ты называешь {i}это{/i} использованием? Не смеши меня!"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:850
translate spanish hwb_s32_4141a230:

    # Mariah "I use those slackers all the time! {i}That’s{/i} using!"
    Mariah "Я использую этих лентяев все время! {i}Вот это{/i} использование!"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:854
translate spanish hwb_s32_e3848df9:

    # Mariah "And ya know what? Who cares? That ditz used you to find the treasure, didn’t she?"
    Mariah "И знаешь че? Да всем насрать! Эта цыпочка использовала тебя, чтобы найти сокровища, разве нет?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:858
translate spanish hwb_s32_bc701f0b:

    # Mariah "Hell, if anything, you probably don’t use her enough! I’d feel like a real {i}jackass{/i} if some {i}dumbass{/i} were coddling me all the time and all I could do was sit there."
    Mariah "Черт, скорее уж ты недостаточно использовала ее! Я бы ощущала себя реальной {i}дурой{/i}, если бы какой-то {i}придурок{/i} все время нянчился со мной, а все что я могла бы делать это сидеть и ничего не делать."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:860
translate spanish hwb_s32_a6098ea5:

    # Mariah "People use people all the time. That’s what makes ‘em family."
    Mariah "Люди используют людей все время. Это то, что делает их семьей."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:864
translate spanish hwb_s32_edf55256:

    # "Mariah takes one last swig of her beer, then with a glint of sadness in her eyes, stares into the empty bottle."
    "Mariah da el último trago a su cerveza, luego, con un destello de tristeza en los ojos, se queda mirando la botella vacía."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:870
translate spanish hwb_s32_a7b083fb:

    # Mariah "So if you’re gonna hate yourself, find a reason that doesn’t suck."
    Mariah "Так что если ты хочешь ненавидеть себя, то хотя бы найди для этого причину, которая не была бы такой убогой."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:879
translate spanish hwb_s32_9e50cfd9:

    # "Her face murks from red to a sickly green. The bottle falls from her hand and onto the floor as she rocks side-to-side, like a sailor that’s lost their sea legs."
    "Su rostro pasa de rojo a un verde enfermizo. La botella se le cae de la mano al suelo mientras se balancea de un lado a otro, como un marinero que ha perdido el equilibrio en el mar."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:883
translate spanish hwb_s32_883e8518:

    # Amber "Hey… You don’t look so good."
    Amber "Эй... Ты выглядишь не очень."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:885
translate spanish hwb_s32_bd3b47ab:

    # "For a quick moment, Mariah’s cheeks bloat out, then just as quickly, she swallows."
    "Por un breve momento, las mejillas de Mariah se inflan, y luego, igual de rápido, ella traga."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:887
translate spanish hwb_s32_515d0614:

    # Mariah "I’m fine. Just need to drink it off."
    Mariah "Я в порядке. Просто нужно допить это."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:893
translate spanish hwb_s32_991ba99c:

    # "She wobbles back to the couch and collapses next to me."
    "Tambaleándose, vuelve al sofá y se desploma a mi lado."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:897
translate spanish hwb_s32_475f2fc8:

    # "Neither of us speak."
    "Ninguna de las dos habla."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:899
translate spanish hwb_s32_bb89b0f3:

    # "Mariah groans, holding her stomach as she feels around for the bottle opener."
    "Mariah gime, sujetándose el estómago mientras busca a tientas el abridor de botellas."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:901
translate spanish hwb_s32_2314ec3f:

    # "I look at the pile of empty bottles building up on the table."
    "Miro el montón de botellas vacías que se acumula en la mesa."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:903
translate spanish hwb_s32_c39583d9:

    # Amber "What happened to not caring?"
    Amber "Что случилось с “мне все равно”?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:907
translate spanish hwb_s32_19f9f683:

    # Mariah "I don’t. I’d just prefer my treasure not being in the filthy hands of an idiot."
    Mariah "Не знаю. Просто я бы предпочла если бы мое сокровище не было в грязных руках какого-то идиота."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:909
translate spanish hwb_s32_055729de:

    # "Did I just get chewed out by Mariah?"
    "¿Acabo de recibir una regañina de Mariah?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:911
translate spanish hwb_s32_a3f45ca0:

    # "Even worse, did some of it actually make sense, or is it just the booze?"
    "Peor aún, ¿tenía algo de sentido, o es solo el alcohol?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:913
translate spanish hwb_s32_a9de8f03:

    # "Unable to spare the energy to lean forward, she stretches her arm way out for another beer, but I catch it just in time and grab ahold of her hand."
    "Sin fuerzas para inclinarse, estira el brazo para alcanzar otra cerveza, pero la atrapo justo a tiempo y tomo su mano."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:917
translate spanish hwb_s32_f5f70acc:

    # Amber "You need to quit. You’ve had way too much."
    Amber "Тебе надо заканчивать. Ты и так уже переборщила."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:921
translate spanish hwb_s32_013e90cd:

    # Mariah "Eat me!"
    Mariah "Поцелуй меня в жопу!"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:923
translate spanish hwb_s32_1892bd12:

    # "She slaps my hand away and snags two more beers, shoving one of them into my stomach."
    "Me aparta la mano de un manotazo y agarra dos cervezas más, metiéndome una en el estómago."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:929
translate spanish hwb_s32_6558b63d:

    # Mariah "You’re an idiot. But whether you wanna keep being one is up to you."
    Mariah "Ты дура. Но зависит от тебя, хочешь ли ты оставаться ей и дальше."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:931
translate spanish hwb_s32_c15e099e:

    # Amber "I… I don’t know. I need to think about it."
    Amber "Я... Я не знаю. Мне надо подумать над этим."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:933
translate spanish hwb_s32_54a3a180:

    # "Mariah rolls her eyes."
    "Mariah pone los ojos en blanco."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:935
translate spanish hwb_s32_9ebcd160:

    # Mariah "Dumbass."
    Mariah "Отбитая."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:937
translate spanish hwb_s32_33302a45:

    # "Nothing she says burns anymore. Now it only stings with the acidity of truth."
    "Nada de lo que dice quema ya. Ahora solo duele con la acidez de la verdad."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:939
translate spanish hwb_s32_af086913:

    # "Getting over it. Letting Marina in—{i}really{/i} letting her in."
    "Superarlo. Dejar entrar a Marina—{i}de verdad{/i} dejarla entrar."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:941
translate spanish hwb_s32_4a4bcec0:

    # "It’s just not that easy."
    "Simplemente no es tan fácil."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:943
translate spanish hwb_s32_75e0cb9a:

    # "It’s never been that easy."
    "Nunca ha sido tan fácil."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:945
translate spanish hwb_s32_7bb23eae:

    # "But if I don’t."
    "Pero si no lo hago."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:949
translate spanish hwb_s32_5de94de0:

    # "Putting my hand on my thigh, I squeeze the outline of the cassette."
    "Poniendo mi mano en el muslo, aprieto el contorno del casete."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:951
translate spanish hwb_s32_4d2458f8:

    # "Mariah raises out her beer and grunts. Sighing, I raise up mine and we clank them together."
    "Mariah levanta su cerveza y gruñe. Suspirando, levanto la mía y las chocamos."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:955
translate spanish hwb_s32_8806f64b:

    # Amber "Jerkass."
    Amber "Сука."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:967
translate spanish hwb_s32_ef7e243b:

    # "Massaging the drunk away, I nurse my head as it pounds in rhythm with my heartbeat."
    "Masajeando la borrachera, me sostengo la cabeza mientras late al ritmo de mi corazón."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:969
translate spanish hwb_s32_06eacb1b:

    # "The table has become a stockpile of empty promises and broken dreams, foundationed beneath even emptier bottles."
    "La mesa se ha convertido en un almacén de promesas vacías y sueños rotos, cimentada bajo botellas aún más vacías."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:971
translate spanish hwb_s32_6057573f:

    # "Mariah is still at my side, slumped over and passed out."
    "Mariah sigue a mi lado, desplomada y desmayada."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:973
translate spanish hwb_s32_6397550c:

    # "She might be a super heavyweight, but I decided to stick around and keep an eye on her."
    "Puede que sea una peso pesado, pero decidí quedarme para vigilarla."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:975
translate spanish hwb_s32_0720436b:

    # "Soon, Joe and Tess will be back and they can take care of the rest."
    "Pronto, Joe y Tess volverán y podrán encargarse del resto."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:977
translate spanish hwb_s32_a5c76770:

    # "I watch the slight movements of her chest as she breaths in and out."
    "Observo los leves movimientos de su pecho mientras inhala y exhala."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:979
translate spanish hwb_s32_75727353:

    # "Seeing her so quiet is eerie. It’s hard to believe there’s still a person underneath all that yelling and obsessiveness. But there she is."
    "Verla tan callada es inquietante. Es difícil creer que todavía haya una persona debajo de todos esos gritos y obsesiones. Pero ahí está."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:981
translate spanish hwb_s32_3abe4374:

    # "‘People use other people all the time. That’s what makes them family.’"
    "\"La gente usa a otras personas todo el tiempo. Eso es lo que las hace familia.\""

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:983
translate spanish hwb_s32_e8874e92:

    # "It sounds gross and awful, but those words have been echoing inside me since she said them."
    "Suena horrible y asqueroso, pero esas palabras han estado resonando dentro de mí desde que las dijo."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:985
translate spanish hwb_s32_ab6904fe:

    # "I used Marina to cope. There’s no denying that. But Mariah said that Marina used me to find the treasure."
    "Usé a Marina para sobrellevarlo. No puedo negarlo. Pero Mariah dijo que Marina me usó a mí para encontrar el tesoro."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:987
translate spanish hwb_s32_7365d975:

    # "If that’s true, then why don’t I feel used? Why did I always feel genuinely wanted by her?"
    "Si eso es cierto, ¿por qué no me siento usada? ¿Por qué siempre sentí que ella realmente me quería?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:989
translate spanish hwb_s32_01e2f74c:

    # "She relied on me. Is that using? That’s all I ever wanted her to feel like she could do. Her trust was the most important thing to me."
    "Ella confiaba en mí. ¿Eso es usar? Eso es todo lo que siempre quise que sintiera que podía hacer. Su confianza era lo más importante para mí."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:991
translate spanish hwb_s32_d1c53229:

    # "But no matter how much I wanted it, I knew I didn’t deserve it. Because I felt like I was betraying Gramps and would just drag her down with me."
    "Pero por mucho que lo deseara, sabía que no lo merecía. Porque sentía que estaba traicionando al Abuelo y que solo la arrastraría conmigo."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:993
translate spanish hwb_s32_8ef57c32:

    # "What about her, though? Marina was furious when I left, be she wanted to understand, she wanted to help."
    "¿Y qué hay de ella? Marina estaba furiosa cuando me fui, pero quería entender, quería ayudar."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:995
translate spanish hwb_s32_f879301c:

    # "I wanted her to rely on me, but maybe she wanted me to rely on her too?"
    "Yo quería que ella confiara en mí, pero ¿quizás ella también quería que yo confiara en ella?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:999
translate spanish hwb_s32_ba857c0e:

    # "Reaching into my pocket, I pull out the cassette and hold it in the palm of my hand."
    "Metiendo la mano en mi bolsillo, saco el casete y lo sostengo en la palma de mi mano."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1001
translate spanish hwb_s32_6673b2a1:

    # "The sight of the ribbon all torn and tangled doesn’t choke me up or ignite a bitter explosion of anger like earlier."
    "Ver la cinta toda rasgada y enredada ya no me ahoga ni enciende una explosión amarga de ira como antes."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1003
translate spanish hwb_s32_fb2b436a:

    # "All it does is serve as a numbing reminder of all my regrets."
    "Todo lo que hace es servir como un recordatorio entumecedor de todos mis arrepentimientos."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1005
translate spanish hwb_s32_f6c5db3d:

    # "Her wording was off, but Mariah was right. I never let myself rely on Marina."
    "Su elección de palabras fue extraña, pero Mariah tenía razón. Nunca me permití confiar en Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1007
translate spanish hwb_s32_81ff389c:

    # "From the very start, I always treated her like a kid and never as an equal."
    "Desde el principio, siempre la traté como a una niña y nunca como a una igual."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1009
translate spanish hwb_s32_64c4cc8d:

    # "No wonder she got upset. She wanted to do as much for me as I was doing for her, but I would never let her in long enough for that to happen."
    "No es de extrañar que se molestara. Ella quería hacer tanto por mí como yo hacía por ella, pero nunca la dejaba entrar el tiempo suficiente para que eso sucediera."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1011
translate spanish hwb_s32_2044e57a:

    # "Of course she wouldn’t say no if I made a move. It was the only opportunity she had."
    "Por supuesto que no diría que no si yo daba el primer paso. Era la única oportunidad que tenía."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1013
translate spanish hwb_s32_4ee61c5a:

    # "If I go back as I am now, things will never get better. I’ll just keep treating Marina like a kid, never letting her in, and she’ll just smile and bear it until she explodes, like earlier."
    "Si vuelvo como estoy ahora, las cosas nunca mejorarán. Seguiré tratando a Marina como a una niña, sin dejarla entrar nunca, y ella solo sonreirá y lo soportará hasta que explote, como antes."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1015
translate spanish hwb_s32_19fa4946:

    # "I know what I have to do, and yet, it feels more like a betrayal thing than anything else I’ve done this far."
    "Sé lo que tengo que hacer y, sin embargo, se siente más como una traición que cualquier otra cosa que haya hecho hasta ahora."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1017
translate spanish hwb_s32_7c64a189:

    # "But if I don’t do it, then I can never truly hope to do right by Marina."
    "Pero si no lo hago, entonces nunca podré esperar realmente hacer lo correcto por Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1023
translate spanish hwb_s32_0538889b:

    # "I stagger to my feet."
    "Me pongo de pie tambaleándome."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1025
translate spanish hwb_s32_93a96c89:

    # "Turning around, I take one last look at Mariah before deciding to take off her bandana and lay her out on her side."
    "Dándome la vuelta, le doy un último vistazo a Mariah antes de decidir quitarme su pañuelo y acostarla de lado."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1029
translate spanish hwb_s32_eefbe141:

    # Amber "In another life, maybe you would be my type."
    Amber "Возможно, в другой жизни ты была бы в моем вкусе."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1034
translate spanish hwb_s32_589d46ef:

    # "Then, I walk to the door, take a breath, and step outside."
    "Luego, camino hacia la puerta, respiro hondo y salgo."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1066
translate spanish hwb_s32_8c2486e1:

    # "The night sky is deep and clear, embedded with a rich blue draped behind the glow of the constellations."
    "El cielo nocturno es profundo y despejado, incrustado en un azul intenso que se extiende detrás del resplandor de las constelaciones."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1068
translate spanish hwb_s32_fd4d1a5b:

    # "Its light is all that guides me as I sludge my way through the thickness of the sand, wandering from Mariah’s RV with a destination of nowhere."
    "Su luz es todo lo que me guía mientras avanzo penosamente entre la espesura de la arena, vagando desde la casa rodante de Mariah sin un destino."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1070
translate spanish hwb_s32_1288ceb2:

    # "Finally, I’ve gone far enough, where the haze of the city lights can’t be seen and where the distances of the motorhome can’t be gauged."
    "Por fin, he llegado lo suficientemente lejos, donde la bruma de las luces de la ciudad no se ve y donde las distancias de la casa rodante no pueden medirse."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1072
translate spanish hwb_s32_0873dddf:

    # "I’m alone. For the first time, I’m truly alone."
    "Estoy sola. Por primera vez, estoy verdaderamente sola."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1074
translate spanish hwb_s32_832e768c:

    # "Free from the treasure, free from the festival, free from the responsibility. Free from even Marina."
    "Libre del tesoro, libre del festival, libre de la responsabilidad. Libre incluso de Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1082
translate spanish hwb_s32_31c548ad:

    # "Sitting down, I sink into the sand and look at the stars."
    "Al sentarme, me hundo en la arena y miro las estrellas."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1086
translate spanish hwb_s32_3e67b096:

    # Amber "Remember that time in Wyoming, when we camped out on the Great Plains?"
    Amber "Помнишь то время в Вайоминге, когда мы разбили лагерь на Великих Равнинах?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1088
translate spanish hwb_s32_7814c1f1:

    # Amber "The whole ‘sleeping under the stars’ thing seemed like the coolest idea ever to little me."
    Amber "Спать под звездами казалось мне самой клевой идеей."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1090
translate spanish hwb_s32_1124abd0:

    # Amber "You were so excited to teach me about the constellations. Didn’t matter that you sucked at astronomy, you just kept mislabeling them."
    Amber "Ты был так рад рассказать мне о созвездиях. Не важно, что ты был очень плох в астрономии и неправильно называл их."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1092
translate spanish hwb_s32_ee1573c5:

    # Amber "I made sure to read up on them later, by the way. That was the Big Dipper, not ‘Howe’s Guitar.’"
    Amber "Я позже читала о них. Это была Большая Медведица, а не “Гитара Хоу”."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1094
translate spanish hwb_s32_7604f8fd:

    # Amber "But that’s okay, I still got a kick out of it."
    Amber "Но все в порядке, я до сих пор рада этому."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1096
translate spanish hwb_s32_004948fd:

    # Amber "Besides, that’s not the type of thing I expected to learn from you anyway."
    Amber "К тому же это не те знания, что я ожидала получить от тебя."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1098
translate spanish hwb_s32_b94185dd:

    # Amber "What I really remember from that trip was the s’mores."
    Amber "Но что я точно помню из той поездки, так это с’мор."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1100
translate spanish hwb_s32_ec1a1b8b:

    # Amber "Pretty sure you only liked them burned because you were so old. Really stuck with me, though. Can’t have s’mores any other way now."
    Amber "Кстати, уверенна, что тебе нравились они в погорелом виде,  потому, что был стар. Но ты реально остался в моей душе. И теперь я сама не могу есть с’мор не в подгорелом виде."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1102
translate spanish hwb_s32_dd2bb5f4:

    # Amber "I think I may have converted someone else to the burned side, too. She has a huge sweet tooth though, so I shouldn’t be too surprised."
    Amber "Но я думаю, я смогла затащить кое-кого еще на темную сторону - на сторону подгоревших маршмэллоу. Но она сладкоежка, так что это не особо удивительно. "

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1104
translate spanish hwb_s32_d4ff37d5:

    # Amber "Still, it made me really happy when she said she liked it."
    Amber "И все же, я была так счастлива, когда она сказала, что ей понравилось."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1106
translate spanish hwb_s32_a7656cd6:

    # "I stare down and pet the cassette, feeling my thumbs over its holes and brown blotches and stains."
    "Bajo la mirada y acaricio el casete, sintiendo mis pulgares sobre sus agujeros, manchas marrones y marcas."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1108
translate spanish hwb_s32_4fb04882:

    # Amber "I think you’d like her a lot."
    Amber "Я думаю, что она бы тебе очень понравилась."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1110
translate spanish hwb_s32_c04eaa65:

    # Amber "She’s a sweetheart, always cheery and nice, even when she really shouldn’t. Don’t know how she does it, but she can somehow deal with me and my moods. Too."
    Amber "Она всегда такая милая, приятная и добрая, даже тогда, когда на самом деле, это было не обязательно. Не знаю, как она это делает, но она каким-то образом умеет сладить со мной и моим настроением."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1112
translate spanish hwb_s32_6a5d65a8:

    # Amber "This is her first time ever leaving home and it shows."
    Amber "Она впервые покинула свой дом и это очень заметно."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1114
translate spanish hwb_s32_37f676d6:

    # Amber "I worry about her a lot."
    Amber "Я очень волнуюсь за нее."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1116
translate spanish hwb_s32_1c3ab648:

    # Amber "Kinda like how I worried about you."
    Amber "Вроде того, как я переживала за тебя."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1120
translate spanish hwb_s32_e6bf5db6:

    # Amber "Kinda like how I still do."
    Amber "Вроде того, как я до сих пор переживаю за тебя."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1122
translate spanish hwb_s32_f3f3939d:

    # "A tear drips onto the cassette. I didn’t even notice it trail down my cheek, or the rest."
    "Una lágrima gotea sobre el casete. Ni siquiera noté cómo bajaba por mi mejilla, ni el resto."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1124
translate spanish hwb_s32_8029aefb:

    # Amber "Maybe I got attached too easily and really did use her, but I don’t want to leave. I love her so much."
    Amber "Может я вела себя слишком легкомысленно, и использовала ее, но я не хочу уходить. Я люблю ее очень сильно."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1126
translate spanish hwb_s32_9ec613d1:

    # Amber "And I want to prove I’m worth loving too."
    Amber "И я хочу доказать, что я заслуживаю любви."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1130
translate spanish hwb_s32_583345e8:

    # Amber "Would you hate me?"
    Amber "Ты возненавидишь меня?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1132
translate spanish hwb_s32_a89282f4:

    # Amber "Would I be letting you down if I decided to be happy instead?"
    Amber "Я бы подвела тебя, если бы решила просто быть счастливой?"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1134
translate spanish hwb_s32_71c30e14:

    # "I gaze back up at the sky through my blurry vision. The stars don’t answer back, they just keep twinkling."
    "Vuelvo a alzar la mirada al cielo con la vista borrosa. Las estrellas no responden, solo siguen titilando."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1136
translate spanish hwb_s32_9d035b50:

    # "I lower my head. The cassette feels like lifeless dead weight in my palm."
    "Bajo la cabeza. El casete se siente como un peso muerto y sin vida en mi palma."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1138
translate spanish hwb_s32_cfcbcd29:

    # "My breath shakes and the next words slip out in a whimper."
    "Mi respiración tiembla y las siguientes palabras se escapan en un gemido."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1140
translate spanish hwb_s32_94e49496:

    # Amber "I’m sorry."
    Amber "Прости меня."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1142
translate spanish hwb_s32_bc78cae6:

    # "I dig my fingers into the ground, scraping away the sand as sharp grains nudge between my nails."
    "Clavo mis dedos en el suelo, raspando la arena mientras granos afilados se meten entre mis uñas."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1144
translate spanish hwb_s32_d11048d3:

    # "A shallow hole forms, a pile of dirt laying next to it."
    "Se forma un hoyo poco profundo, con un montón de tierra al lado."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1146
translate spanish hwb_s32_758a698e:

    # "I can barely stomach looking at the cassette as I lay it down in its grave. I glance away as I slide the dirt back over the hole."
    "Apenas puedo soportar mirar el casete mientras lo coloco en su tumba. Desvío la mirada mientras deslizo la tierra de vuelta sobre el hoyo."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1148
translate spanish hwb_s32_fb45c76d:

    # "When I look back, a corner of it still sticks out, only partially buried. It’s reaching out, grasping for me."
    "Cuando vuelvo a mirar, una esquina aún sobresale, solo parcialmente enterrada. Se extiende, aferrándose a mí."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1150
translate spanish hwb_s32_82205b44:

    # "I cover my eyes and pinch away the tears. It’s still there, it will always be there, but now I don’t have to acknowledge it."
    "Me cubro los ojos y aprieto para contener las lágrimas. Sigue ahí, siempre estará ahí, pero ahora no tengo que reconocerlo."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1152
translate spanish hwb_s32_94e49496_1:

    # Amber "I’m sorry."
    Amber "Прости."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1154
translate spanish hwb_s32_f9bfddb1:

    # Amber "I’m sorry…"
    Amber "Прости меня…"

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:977
translate spanish hwb_s32_46d59c46:

    # "I watch the slight movements of her chest as she breathes in and out."
    "Observo los ligeros movimientos de su pecho mientras inhala y exhala."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:993
translate spanish hwb_s32_f3cf4da5:

    # "What about her, though? Marina was furious when I left, but she wanted to understand, she wanted to help."
    "¿Y qué hay de ella, entonces? Marina estaba furiosa cuando me fui, pero quería entender, quería ayudar."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:541
translate spanish hwb_s32_7090aa1b:

    # "She’s a maniac; that has always been, and still is, abundantly clear. She probably {i}would{/i} tear apart the entire Southwest if left unattended. Hell, maybe even the entire nation."
    "Es una maníaca; eso siempre ha sido, y sigue siendo, abundantemente claro. Probablemente {i}destrozaría{/i} todo el Suroeste si la dejaran sola. Demonios, tal vez incluso toda la nación."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:1110
translate spanish hwb_s32_3eb32a75:

    # Amber "She’s a sweetheart, always cheery and nice, even when she really shouldn’t. Don’t know how she does it, but she can somehow deal with me and my moods."
    Amber "Она всегда такая милая, приятная и добрая, даже тогда, когда на самом деле, это было не обязательно. Не знаю, как она это делает, но она каким-то образом умеет сладить со мной и моим настроением."

# game/script/hwb_s32.rpy:513
translate spanish hwb_s32_4b762d20:

    # "The swampy drink trails down my throat, setting my chest on fire."
    "La bebida pantanosa baja por mi garganta, incendiando mi pecho."

